  <string name="settings_service_clean">Marshrutlash qoidalarini tozalash/qayta qo‘llash</string>
  <string name="settings_service_clean_summary">O‘zgargan sozlamalarni joriy faol xizmatlarga qo‘llash. Kam uchraydigan race condition holatlarini ham tuzatishi mumkin.</string>
  <string name="settings_system_tether_offload">Modem rejimida apparatli tezlashtirish</string>
  <string name="settings_system_tether_offload_summary">Tizim Developer options bo‘limiga yorliq. System tethering ustida VPN tethering uchun buni o‘chirish ko‘pincha kerak bo‘ladi, ammo tethering faol bo‘lganda batareya vaqtini kamaytirishi mumkin.</string>
